>\n身處英國的鄭文傑，目睹香港的情況每下愈況，在新年之際，寄語港人要珍惜每個值得感恩及開心的時刻，「喺香港面對住非常大嘅壓力，因為係面對成個威權體制擴張嘅最前線，本身係好不對稱嘅抗爭，所以我哋唔應該因為嗰種緊張、憂鬱、壓抑而拖垮自己，我哋一定要保存自己，喺一啲生活上嘅小細節去感受到快樂。可以休息，但唔可以放棄，可以暫時失望，但唔應該絕望」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210215/ICKPA3UMCRG77LSPYQC2FFVIJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210215%2FICKPA3UMCRG77LSPYQC2FFVIJI%2F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eVTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=4f19e97d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210215%2FICKPA3UMCRG77LSPYQC2FFVIJI%2F&h=caced891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210215/ICKPA3UMCRG77LSPYQC2FFVIJI/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多手足在囚都無得團聚"},{"pid":"09d3d1c40c4a51a01308ee688e153ceeb8c9c5e2","tid":2408257,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ec953ff38d09ab816438effe74779d9b66dd196","tid":2408257,"uid":226851,"like":0,"dislike":37,"score":-37,"quote":{"pid":"2dbb8dde9a84183903051d64570f876f6014381e","tid":2408257,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T18:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LZ9Dc18OuxMZTJG7Tbw2qBoK6Ls=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H5U2EPYXWRGPZOACTU6FS62EWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLZ9Dc18OuxMZTJG7Tbw2qBoK6Ls%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH5U2EPYXWRGPZOACTU6FS62EWI.jpg&h=008b8734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭文傑記得去年的新年仍有跟家人聯絡，但之後他向中文媒體詳述遭中方扣留的經過，因擔心家人安危，無奈宣佈與家人斷絕關係。在這之前，每逢農曆新年，他都會與家人到深圳過年及探親，「𢭃利是、玩炮仗，會幾難得一家團聚嘅日子，但呢啲都係回憶啦，今時今日唔好話大陸返唔到去，連香港都返唔到，唔知幾時可以再見返」。<br />\n<br />\n因為政權而被迫斷絕關係，無法再聯絡，想起已經年屆70歲的父母，鄭不禁感觸，「唔知道未來有冇機會，喺有生之年再見番佢哋，𠵱家每到新年都有好大感觸，但都冇辦法啦，希望佢哋知道我喺度一切正常、安好，唔需要擔